dBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T00:38:30.000Z","msg":"明明成篇文章前段都有意思<br />\n最尾居然係叫學生組織議和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同投降有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09d25b4c3c6b7d2a907def0724097fc6013dda04","tid":1775294,"uid":336896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T00:47:31.000Z","msg":"當年國共內戰，<br />\n美國嘅馬歇爾迫蔣介石要同毛賊東和談，<br />\n白崇禧喺東北本來幾乎大勝，被迫停止追擊，<br />\n令林彪軍隊可以重整旗鼓。<br />\n結果之後共產黨立即反口反攻，<br />\n國民黨就兵敗如山倒。<br />\n杜魯門同馬歇爾根本就係害死中華民國嘅幫兇!<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">和談你老母!</span></span>"}]}